data.description: JUST REDUCED!! Look no further! This beautiful 3 bedroom 2 bath pool/spa home has everything you need for your new home including a bonus 4th bedroom that can used as a bedroom, office, or in-law quarters. Features include new A/C, new water heater, new hurricane impact windows, new pavers around the pool, new pool pump, upgraded kitchen with stainless steal appliances, circular driveway, and much more. This house is situated on a dead end street with a cul-de-sac for privacy. This will be gone fast!
